node.text: merry Christmas and happy holidays everyone! I hope you all have an amazing day with your loved ones ❤️ I feel so grateful today that my family is together and healthy and that is all that matters to me. My grandma is 91 years old and unfortunately took a tumble last night and was rushed to the emergency room but she is fine and living her best life! Things like that really make me rethink the important things in life and i am forever grateful to be able to continue these traditions with my family and newfound loved ones ❤️ count your blessings and have the best day

While @amfar has made significant progress in the fight against #aids , nearly 38 million people worldwide are living with #hiv. 1.7 million of these people are sadly children. The AIDS epidemic is still not over and this poses a new risk for our generation. amfAR has created generationCURE, a group of young amfAR supporters who can bring awareness and hopefully find a cure for the AIDS pandemic in our lifetime. I want to be a part of the generation that brings the AIDS epidemic to an end once and for all. Supporting events like the generationCURE holiday party last night, enables amfAR to advance the research that will one day cure HIV.
